# Project README

## Overview

This project is a simple demonstration project. It currently includes a file named `test.txt`.

## Getting Started

1. **Clone the repository:**
   ```
   git clone <your-repo-url>
   ```
2. **Navigate to the project directory:**
   ```
   cd <your-project-directory>
   ```

## Project Structure

```
test.txt
```

## Files

- **test.txt**: Contains a single line of random characters.

